# ============================================
# LLM API Configuration
# ============================================
# Choose ONE of the following options:

# Option 1: Azure OpenAI or Custom Gateway (e.g., enterprise endpoint)
# Uncomment and fill these if using Azure OpenAI or a custom LLM gateway:
# MY_LLM_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
# MY_LLM_ENDPOINT=https://your-endpoint.openai.azure.com/
# MY_LLM_API_VERSION=2024-10-21

# Option 2: Standard OpenAI (easiest for testing)
# Uncomment and fill this if using standard OpenAI:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# ============================================
# Notes:
# - Copy this file to .env and add your real credentials
# - Never commit .env to version control
# - The app will automatically detect which option you configured
# ============================================

